  number    = {Wainberg, M, & Dixon, L (2017). Ending HIV, hepatitis B, and hepatitis C: what about people with severe mental illness?. Lancet Psychiatry, 4, 651-653. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S2215-0366(17)30282-1},
